BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Launchpad 2.0 - BlerdMan
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260714T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260714T214500
DTSTAMP:20260714T051736Z
UID:occ-1003@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:An early look at a new play in development\, part of Theatrica
 l Outfit's Launchpad 2.0 new-works festival.\n\nA new play getting an earl
 y public showing as part of Launchpad 2.0\, Theatrical Outfit's developmen
 t series for work still being built. It is one of four new plays performin
 g in rotation across the festival\, alongside The Penelopes\, Queen (of th
 e American Nail Salon)\, and I'm a Mother Fucking Superstar. Performances 
 of BlerdMan run through July 25.
GEO:33.757035;-84.389486
LAST-MODIFIED:20260714T051315Z
LOCATION:Theatrical Outfit\, 84 Luckie St NW
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
