BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Children
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270609T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270609T213000
DTSTAMP:20260714T051736Z
UID:occ-1056@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Lucy Kirkwood's darkly comic thriller: two retired nuclear phy
 sicists\, a colleague back after 38 years\, and old debts coming due.\n\nI
 n a cottage on the British coast\, two married\, retired nuclear physicist
 s live quietly in the wake of a disaster. Then a former colleague reappear
 s after 38 years\, and the couple's careful equilibrium starts to crack. L
 ucy Kirkwood's 2016 thriller\, funnier than its premise suggests\, asks wh
 at one generation owes the one that follows\; it was a hit in London and o
 n Broadway\, and in 2019 Guardian writers ranked it third among the greate
 st theatrical works since 2000. Presented by Theatrical Outfit.
GEO:33.757035;-84.389486
LAST-MODIFIED:20260714T051315Z
LOCATION:Theatrical Outfit\, 84 Luckie St NW
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
